amme had overwhelmingly resulted in their school delivering tennis or more tennis. \n-\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; \n95% of schools who took part in the survey (1,335 schools) are drawn \nfrom the state sector and the vast majority (95%) agree \nthat the programme \nis\n helping to make tennis more inclusive and accessible for their pupils.\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nSeptember 2013\n&#xa0;\n"